wiki.content:
Following on from the success of the No.1 summer smash “Spectrum” Harris' single “Sweet Nothing” which features guest vocals from Florence Welch shot straight to the top of the UK singles chart in Oct 2012. This marked Harris' first No.1 single as a main artist in the UK since “I'm Not Alone” in 2009.
